title.narrative: Number of villages connected by bus service on completed Project roads /8
Rural Transport Component:Number of villages connected by completed Project roads /7
Implementation of a new debt management system
Institutional Development Component:Implementation of a new rural road maintenance system
Rural Transport component:Reduction in travel time on a 25% sample of Project roads

comment.narrative: Reduction in travel time exceeded target value (positive outcome).

The travel time through G321 was reduced as compared with the previous year but not to the level as expected. It was because moreheavy trucks and lorries carried construction materials via G321 to Longdongbao Area which was under expansion and development. Theheavy trucks caused slower travel speed and prolonged travel time.
Traffic volume exceeded target value (positive outcome).

Guiyang Area development intensified, and traffic has increased, especially Shuangqiaoshan truck driving on State Road 321, and theother local farmers agricultural vehicles as well – thus, there is a small increase in travel time.
